column2:
"Thank you! You have completed the
request that I have given you.
You are so professional!"

"However ...it's regrettable that there
ain't much drastic differences that I felt."

"Anyway, I think it will be more fun to
think of the various cooking methods
by using this. "

"Please help me again when the time
comes!"

"ありがとう！
依頼された仕事をきちんとこなす。
さすがプロよね！"

"ただ……思ったほど劇的な違いが
なさそうな感じなのが残念。"

"まあでも、これはこれで色々と調理法を
考える楽しみが増えたしね！"
"また、なにかあった時はよろしくね！"
